# Title: Nslookup PowerShell Download Cradle
# Author: Sai Prashanth Pulisetti @pulisettis, Aishwarya Singam
# Date: 2022-12-10
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects a powershell download cradle using nslookup. This cradle uses nslookup to extract payloads from DNS records.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_classic/posh_pc_abuse_nslookup_with_dns_records.yml

Data IN ("*-q=txt http*", "*-querytype=txt http*", "*-type=txt http*") Data="*powershell*" Data="*nslookup*" Data="*[1]*"